==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Touchy
<hw>Touch"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[For <ets>techy</ets>,
<ets>tetchy</ets>.]</ety> <def>Peevish; irritable; irascible; techy; apt
to take fire.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It may be said of Dryden that he was at no time <qex>touchy</qex>
about personal attacks.</q> <rj><qau>Saintsbury.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tough</ent>⟦br⟧
